{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "03", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "16", "M": "33", "S": "12"}}, "news": [{"title": "Prime Offices Fund acquires 51% stake in 1.1 million sq ft office asset in Pune", "para": "PRIME Offices Fund has acquired a significant stake in a large office development in Pune. This move expands PRIME's office portfolio to nearly 3.8 million square feet. The fund manager, NCW, is a joint venture between Nuvama Asset Management and Cushman & Wakefield. This follows a recent major acquisition in Chennai.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/prime-offices-fund-acquires-51-stake-in-major-pune-office-development/128975721?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-132508/128975721.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "The evolution of home loan insurance in India", "para": "In India, home loan insurance is undergoing a transformation. It has become an essential financial ally for homeowners. With more affordable options, borrowers can now shield their families from the burden of debt. The ability to personalize coverage allows individuals to tailor protection to their unique circumstances.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/blog/the-evolution-of-home-loan-insurance-in-india/128960342?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-25992/128960342.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "the-evolution-of-home-loan-insurance-in-india"}, {"title": "Ahmedabad development body can now allow development in agri zone at Gokuldham", "para": "After a dispute suspended permissions in 2014, the Ahmedabad Urban Development Authority chairman can now issue development and revised development permissions for agricultural land within the Gokuldham township. This authority covers over 10 lakh square metres in Sanand taluka, following a decade-long approval process for the township's layout and subsequent land integrations.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/auda-empowers-gokuldham-development-after-12-year-delay/128958030?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-159844/128958030.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}